Continuous Monitoring --> why?

uptime
health check
performance metrics --> response time (latency), errors/exceptions, resource utilisation
troubleshoot applications

role of a devops engineer
1. perform POC
2. setup/install monitoring tools
3. create dashboards for various metrics --> cpu, memory, disk iops, status code, ..
4. setup alerts

Prometheus & Grafana

1. Database --> Prometheus
2. visualization tool --> Grafana
3. Agents --> node exporter
